Package: clamprotect
Version: 1.0.1-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: ClamProtect Team <team@clamprotect.local>
Installed-Size: 177
Depends: python3:any, python3-pyqt6, clamav-daemon | clamav, python3-nautilus (>= 4.0) | nautilus-python
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/clamprotect/clamprotect
Description: Modern ClamAV GUI — Real-time malware protection
 ClamProtect brings a modern graphical interface to ClamAV.
 It offers on-demand scanning, real-time file monitoring,
 scheduled scans, quarantine management, and system tray
 integration — all without requiring a server daemon.
 .
 Features:
  * On-demand drag-and-drop scanning
  * Real-time file monitoring with auto-quarantine
  * Scheduled scans via crontab
  * Quarantine management (restore / delete)
  * Scan history with stats cards
  * Dark & Light themes
  * System tray background operation
